<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #000;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #FFF9E6;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .header {
      background: #FFE500;
      border: 4px solid #000;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 4px 4px 0px 0px #000;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .content {
      border: 4px solid #000;
      border-top: 0;
      padding: 24px;
      background: #fff;
      box-shadow: 4px 4px 0px 0px #000;
    }
    .field {
      margin-bottom: 16px;
      padding-bottom: 16px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #eee;
    }
    .field:last-child {
      border-bottom: none;
      margin-bottom: 0;
      padding-bottom: 0;
    }
    .label {
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 12px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }
    .value {
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .message-content {
      background: #f5f5f5;
      padding: 16px;
      border: 2px solid #000;
      margin-top: 8px;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      color: #666;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      background: #00F5D4;
      border: 2px solid #000;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>새로운 문의가 도착했습니다</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <div class="field">
        <div class="label">문의 유형</div>
        <div class="value">
          <span class="badge"><%= @contact.inquiry_type_label %></span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <div class="label">이름</div>
        <div class="value"><%= @contact.name %></div>
      </div>

      <div class="field">
        <div class="label">이메일</div>
        <div class="value"><%= @contact.email %></div>
      </div>

      <% if @contact.company.present? %>
        <div class="field">
          <div class="label">회사</div>
          <div class="value"><%= @contact.company %></div>
        </div>
      <% end %>

      <div class="field">
        <div class="label">메시지</div>
        <div class="message-content">
          <%= simple_format(@contact.message) %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>이 이메일은 Cukee 웹사이트에서 자동 발송되었습니다.</p>
      <p>&copy; <%= Date.current.year %> playwith404</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
